"Ramp" is a Gambling term for betting exchange Betfair.com. Because betfair is a betting exchange, odds are chosen by punters rather than a bookmaker. A Ramp is false, or misleading information in order to get a particular betting price to change odds, for the advantage of the "Ramper"

Common usage results from comments and speculation regarding change in Sports Management, Specialist Bets such as TV and Entertainment or even regular sporting games, for instance posting incorrect team sheets.